descript.abstract: This data set represents current county boundaries in Utah at 1:24,000 scale. Includes changes to the Salt Lake & Utah Counties (Draper Ridgeline) in 2005 and changes to the Emery & Grand Counties (Green River) in 2002.
descript.purpose: This data set represents county boundaries in Utah at 1:24,000 scale.
descript.supplinf: The Utah Office of the USDA Soil Conservation Service, renamed the National Resource Conservation Service (NRCS), digitized the data. The source was USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle paper maps. It is also the tile index for all directories with county tile units.
